'''Ban Ki-moon''' ([[Hôn-koet-ngî]]: 반기문/潘基文 ''Phan Kî-vùn'', {{bd|1944-ngièn|6-ngie̍t 13-ngit||}}), thi-pat ngim khi̍p hien-ngim chṳ̂ [[Lièn-ha̍p-koet Pi-sû-chóng]], [[Hôn-koet]] ngoi-kâu-kôn, chṳn-chhṳ-kâ. 2006-ngièn 10-ngie̍t 9-ngit, [[Lièn-ha̍p-koet Ôn-chhiòn Lî-sṳ-fi]] thèu-phiàu thûng-ko Ban Ki-moon chiap-thoi [[Kofi Annan]]. 2006-ngièn 10-ngie̍t 19-ngit, Ban Ki-moon hiong Hôn-koet chúng-thúng [[Roh Moo-hyun]] thì-kâu Hôn-koet ngoi-kâu thûng-sông phu-chóng-kôn chṳt-vi ke chhṳ̀-chhṳ̀n. Kì he thi-ngi vi [[Â-chû]] ke [[Lièn-ha̍p-koet Pi-sû-chóng]]. 2007-ngièn 1-ngie̍t 1-ngit chhut-ngim Lièn-ha̍p-koet Pi-sû-chóng yit-chṳt. 2011-ngièn 6-ngie̍t 21-ngit, chhai thi 65-kài Lièn-ha̍p-koet Thai-fi sông tet-chho̍k lien-ngim, ngim-khì chṳ 2016-ngièn 12-ngie̍t 31-ngit.

